Embodiments of the invention will now be described with reference to the accompanying drawings, in which:
Figure 1 illustrates an aircraft wing showing the area of interest for thermal testing;
Figure 2 illustrates a section side view of a partial wing box test specimen for the wing of Figure 1, and which shows the thermal test area;
Figure 3 illustrates a plan view of the partial wing box with a thermal shroud installed;
Figures 4a and 4b illustrate views of the thermal shroud showing upper and lower sections of the shroud joined together;
Figure 5 illustrates the partial wing box mounted in a test rig (some parts removed for clarity) with the thermal shroud installed;
Figure 6 illustrates a partial cut away view of the upper section of the thermal shroud installed on the partial wing box and showing a sealed opening to permit the wing box to penetrate the shroud;
Figure 7 illustrates a section view of the sealing arrangement shown in Figure 6 with the drawstring slack; and
Figure 8 illustrates a section view of the sealing arrangement shown in Figure 6 with the drawstring pulled tight.
